==Building Trains==
To build a [[en/Manual/Trains]], place a train [[en/Manual/Depots]] and then click it. You will be presented with the depot window. Select "Build new vehicles". A new window should pop up with a list of different trains to purchase. Select one you think will be necessary, and then press "Buy Vehicle" at the bottom of this window. The train will then appear in one of the slots in the depot window and a window will pop up. Now that you have added the engine, you must add wagons or vans. To do this, use the Build new vehicles window to choose a wagon or a van suitable for what you want to carry. Once you have, select it and press "Buy vehicle". Repeat as many times as you need, bearing in mind it is two vehicles to a square. Give it orders or refit it as necessary, and then click on the red "Stopped" text to start it!

